SUMMARY:Deadline: Heart2World Publishing: Heart2World Book Prize 2026 (Inau
 gural\, Poetry)
DESCRIPTION:The inaugural Heart2World Book Prize\, from Heart2World Publish
 ing\, is a poetry prize for a full-length collection by a Nigerian writer.
  AWARD: NGN 250\,000 cash prize\, a full publishing and marketing package 
 (valued at approximately NGN 5 million)\, and 100 percent net royalties on
  the published collection. ELIGIBILITY: Nigerian citizens currently residi
 ng in Nigeria\; submit an unpublished poetry collection of 30 to 35 poems 
 written in English. There is no entry or reading fee (verified on the fund
 er page). DEADLINE: 5 August 2026. Apply via the prize page.\n\nOrganisati
 on: Heart2World Publishing\nLocation: Nigeria\; open to Nigerian writers c
 urrently residing in Nigeria.\nAward: NGN 250\,000 cash prize\, a full pub
 lishing and marketing package (valued at approximately NGN 5 million)\, an
 d 100 percent net royalties on the published collection. No entry or readi
 ng fee.\nDuration: One-off prize\; publication to follow\n\nMore: https://
 heart2worldpublishing.org/prize/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm
 _medium=referral
URL:https://heart2worldpublishing.org/prize/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugr
 antdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Nigeria\; open to Nigerian writers currently residing in Nigeria.
END:VEVENT
