 wiss literature through book fairs\, group publisher appearances\, and lit
 erary festivals. Open to event organizers\, publishing houses\, profession
 al associations\, and digital platforms based in Switzerland with regular 
 artistic activity there. ELIGIBILITY: requires a connection to Switzerland
