 y in Switzerland)\; not open to practitioners without a Swiss connection. 
 AMOUNT: maximum CHF 25\,000. Deadlines twice a year: 1 March (23:59 CET) a
 nd 1 September (23:59 CEST). Apply via the Pro Helvetia portal.\n\nOrganis
 ation: Pro Helvetia (Swiss Arts Council)\nLocation: Event organizers\, pub
 lishing houses\, professional associations\, and digital platforms based i
 n Switzerland.\nAward: Maximum CHF 25\,000. No application fee.\nDuration:
